author: marvin
msg: Probe for "inline" keyword using "static inline" variant, since that was never
an area of conflict for GCC (unlike the semantics of straight-up "inline",
which were inconsistent between GNU and C99).  Test "__inline" keyword first,
since GCC understands it and that's the one MSVC wants.
